## Skymarket Project Structure

- Entry: `app/layout.tsx` and route segments under `app/*`
- API & middleware: `app/api/*`, `middleware.ts`
- Supabase SQL: [`supabase/schema.sql`](mdc:supabase/schema.sql), migrations in `supabase/migrations/*`
- Types: [`types/database.ts`](mdc:types/database.ts)
- Utilities: [`lib/utils.ts`](mdc:lib/utils.ts)
- UI: `components/**` with `components/layout/SiteHeader.tsx`
- Config: [`package.json`](mdc:package.json), [`tsconfig.json`](mdc:tsconfig.json), [`eslint.config.mjs`](mdc:eslint.config.mjs)

Conventions:
- Use absolute imports via `@/*` (see `tsconfig.json` paths)
- Prefer Server Components by default; mark client with `'use client'`
- Keep routes colocated: e.g., `app/browse/[category]/page.tsx`